The paper discusses the intersection of software engineering and operations, which is the focus of the cs.SE sub-category. It also touches on distributed systems and scalability, which are relevant to the cs.DC sub-category. The use of tools and automation in the DevOps pipeline relates to the cs.PL sub-category. The survey methodology and data analysis could fall under the cs.SD sub-category. Finally, the use of performance analysis tools in industry could be relevant to the cs.NI sub-category, which focuses on networked and internet-based systems.
